  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *Confluence Server*. Using *Confluence Cloud*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/CONFCLOUD-8421].
  {panel}

This blog post seems to indicate so:

http://java.stake-online.com/blog/2007/04/glassfish-v2-and-atlassians-jira-and.html

We should download Glassfish V2 and run the functional and unit tests against it. Ideally, add a Bamboo build.

The README.txt contains the following line 'Errors' section:
{quote}
If you encounter any errors, please report them to support
(mailto:confluence-support@atlassian.com).
{quote}
The official policy is now to point users to support.atlassian.com, where they can find links to more information or create a support issue.

