From watching a new Atlassian employee sit down at Confluence - the first attempt to create their personal space went via the big "Create Space" button on the dashboard.

If a user has permission to create a personal space, and has not yet created one, they should be given the chance to from the global Create Space page (possibly via. a drop-down?)

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
