It would be convenient to have tabs at the bottom of the page for switching between Rich Text, Wiki Markup, and Preview modes. This would be especially useful when in preview mode. Currently, to preview content you added to the document, you must click preview, scroll to the bottom of the page, scroll back up to the top, and click back to Rich Text or Wiki Markup to make more changes. When proofreading a long document, it makes for a lot of scrolling back and forth.

